So my doctor said

00:57.140 --> 00:59.100
I only have to wear

00:59.142 --> 01:01.102
these special shoes

00:59.142 --> 01:01.102
for two more years.

01:01.144 --> 01:03.146
Then I'm down to

01:01.144 --> 01:03.146
nights and weekends.

