08:54.826 --> 08:56.411
Mom, wake up.

08:56.453 --> 08:57.578
Take the children.

08:57.620 --> 08:58.663
Just let me live.

08:58.705 --> 09:00.748
Remember, I didn't want

08:58.705 --> 09:00.748
