09:04.627 --> 09:07.255
I've actually

09:04.627 --> 09:07.255
called the police

09:04.627 --> 09:07.255
on my own mother.

09:07.297 --> 09:08.589
They're here

09:07.297 --> 09:08.589
to cart you away.

09:08.631 --> 09:11.843
How could you do this to me?!

09:11.885 --> 09:14.012
After everything I've done

09:11.885 --> 09:14.012
for you?

09:14.054 --> 09:15.596
We're family, for God's sake!

09:15.638 --> 09:17.224
Good. You're here.

09:17.265 --> 09:18.599
That's them.

09:17.265 --> 09:18.599
Get 'em out of here.

09:18.641 --> 09:19.851
What?!

09:19.893 --> 09:21.269
They've been

09:19.893 --> 09:21.269
stealing from me.

09:21.311 --> 09:22.603
I want them out

09:21.311 --> 09:22.603
of my house.

09:22.645 --> 09:23.646
Wait a minute.

09:23.688 --> 09:24.814
No, this is my house!

