10:24.874 --> 10:27.127
on that old lady's

10:24.874 --> 10:27.127
head, I'll be back.

10:27.168 --> 10:29.629
Off duty.

10:44.727 --> 10:46.146
Pass the rolls.

10:52.569 --> 10:54.695
You think that bothers me?

10:56.739 --> 11:00.201
Guess why your soup

10:56.739 --> 11:00.201
tasted different

11:00.243 --> 11:02.036
when you came back

11:00.243 --> 11:02.036
from bathroom.

