Ugh.

11:05.624 --> 11:07.334
There has to

11:05.624 --> 11:07.334
be some way to

11:05.624 --> 11:07.334
get rid of her.

11:07.375 --> 11:08.918
Well, we know

11:07.375 --> 11:08.918
