11:08.960 --> 11:10.711
Let's just face it.

11:08.960 --> 11:10.711
We're stuck with her.

11:10.753 --> 11:11.796
You can't give up.

11:11.838 --> 11:13.507
You can

11:11.838 --> 11:13.507
