11:33.860 --> 11:35.654
Abe, um...

11:35.694 --> 11:37.238
It-it has to do

11:35.694 --> 11:37.238
with my mother.

11:37.280 --> 11:39.449
Oh, I know about mothers.

11:37.280 --> 11:39.449
Every time

11:39.491 --> 11:40.534
mine comes over

11:39.491 --> 11:40.534
