12:46.099 --> 12:47.475
Can we discuss this later?

12:47.517 --> 12:48.435
I'm with friends.

12:48.476 --> 12:49.185
Give me the tux.

12:49.227 --> 12:50.604
What?

12:50.645 --> 12:51.812
Thank you.

12:50.645 --> 12:51.812
No!

12:51.854 --> 12:54.107
I like this tux.

12:51.854 --> 12:54.107
It's mine.

12:54.148 --> 12:56.817
It's not yours. Now give it

12:54.148 --> 12:56.817
back, or I'll call security.

12:56.859 --> 12:58.737
Hey, I'm over there!

12:58.777 --> 12:59.820
Hey... you...

12:59.862 --> 13:01.030
Hey!

13:01.072 --> 13:02.323
Tell me which

13:01.072 --> 13:02.323
one you like.

13:02.365 --> 13:03.658
And be honest.

13:03.700 --> 13:04.825
Dad, I just want to know.

13:04.867 --> 13:06.827
Do you have any kind

13:04.867 --> 13:06.827
of financial plan at all?

13:06.869 --> 13:07.828
Any plan

13:06.869 --> 13:07.828
about anything?

13:07.870 --> 13:08.996
Malcolm, I'm telling

13:07.870 --> 13:08.996
you for the last time,

13:09.038 --> 13:10.498
stop worrying

13:09.038 --> 13:10.498
about money.

