13:16.045 --> 13:18.005
You guys are going to

13:16.045 --> 13:18.005
be at least 70 bucks

13:18.047 --> 13:19.257
in the hole

13:18.047 --> 13:19.257
every month.

13:19.299 --> 13:21.008
By the time the baby

13:19.299 --> 13:21.008
starts school,

13:21.050 --> 13:22.843
you're going to be $18,000

13:21.050 --> 13:22.843
in debt,

13:22.885 --> 13:24.845
