16:15.850 --> 16:17.017
This would be a good time

16:17.059 --> 16:19.520
for one of those ideas

16:17.059 --> 16:19.520
we were talking about.

16:19.562 --> 16:21.481
I've got nothing.

16:21.522 --> 16:23.399
LOIS:

16:21.522 --> 16:23.399
Thank you so much

16:21.522 --> 16:23.399
