16:23.441 --> 16:25.485
I know this is

16:23.441 --> 16:25.485
a little weird.

16:25.526 --> 16:26.820
Actually, I'm kind of excited.

16:26.861 --> 16:28.279
This is kind of like

16:28.321 --> 16:30.865
when I did  Spoon River Anthology

16:28.321 --> 16:30.865
