17:37.724 --> 17:39.475
Mom, these are our neighbors.

17:39.517 --> 17:41.101
Steve lives next door.

17:41.143 --> 17:42.102
Malik is on the other side.

17:42.144 --> 17:44.397
And Trey lives

17:42.144 --> 17:44.397
