Allow me.

18:02.248 --> 18:03.958
Well, hello.

18:04.000 --> 18:06.502
And who is this fine lady?

18:06.544 --> 18:07.712
So what you doing

18:07.754 --> 18:09.088
later on?

18:09.797 --> 18:12.174
'Cause I like that wagon

18:12.216 --> 18:14.301
you draggin'.

18:14.343 --> 18:18.347
(screaming)

18:18.389 --> 18:22.602
