18:29.901 --> 18:31.151
or a Dumpster.

18:31.193 --> 18:32.361
Well, there's

18:31.193 --> 18:32.361
obviously

18:32.403 --> 18:34.822
nothing I can do

18:32.403 --> 18:34.822
to change your mind,

18:34.864 --> 18:36.156
