18:36.198 --> 18:38.325
You only just

18:36.198 --> 18:38.325
got here. I...

18:38.367 --> 18:40.160
What's wrong with you?

18:40.202 --> 18:42.747
Nothing.

18:42.789 --> 18:44.874
Everything is perfectly fine.

18:47.251 --> 18:49.087
Francis,

18:49.128 --> 18:50.379
you have to listen

18:49.128 --> 18:50.379
