18:59.221 --> 19:00.347
Come on, Ida.

18:59.221 --> 19:00.347
Let me help you.

19:00.389 --> 19:02.182
Don't you have

19:00.389 --> 19:02.182
rain dance to do?

19:02.224 --> 19:03.225
Bye, Mom.

19:03.267 --> 19:04.226
Great to see you.

19:04.268 --> 19:05.853
Have a safe trip.

19:05.895 --> 19:08.230
Don't forget to call us

19:05.895 --> 19:08.230
whenever you get to...

19:08.272 --> 19:10.190
wherever...

19:10.232 --> 19:11.233
(water splashing on floor)

19:11.275 --> 19:13.152
(all gasp)

19:15.947 --> 19:18.240
Maybe I'll stay

19:15.947 --> 19:18.240
few more minutes.

19:18.282 --> 19:20.952
