19:27.249 --> 19:28.918
Well, Dewey,

19:27.249 --> 19:28.918
I hope you're happy.

19:28.960 --> 19:31.211
I thought I would be,

19:28.960 --> 19:31.211
but not  this  much.

19:31.253 --> 19:33.422
Let's find Reese

19:31.253 --> 19:33.422
and get out of here.

