Why is my cell

19:33.464 --> 19:35.466
phone off?

19:35.508 --> 19:38.719
68 messages?!

19:38.761 --> 19:40.054
ABE:

19:38.761 --> 19:40.054
The contraction started

19:40.096 --> 19:41.221
