Now, honey,

19:52.150 --> 19:53.484
I don't want you

19:52.150 --> 19:53.484
to get too excited,

19:53.526 --> 19:55.153
but I think you should

19:53.526 --> 19:55.153
come home now,

19:55.194 --> 19:56.236
because, I'm... well, I'm...

19:56.278 --> 19:58.238
(laughs):

19:56.278 --> 19:58.238
I'm having the baby.

19:58.280 --> 19:59.323
What?!

19:59.365 --> 20:00.533
O... kay.

20:00.574 --> 20:01.868
Well, just... stay calm, too.

20:01.909 --> 20:04.244
Yeah, getting worked up

20:01.909 --> 20:04.244
will only accelerate things.

20:04.286 --> 20:05.245
Just relax.

20:05.287 --> 20:06.413
Do your breathing.

20:06.455 --> 20:07.665
(laughs)

20:07.707 --> 20:09.249
Where the hell

20:07.707 --> 20:09.249
is Reese?

20:07.707 --> 20:09.249
What's wrong?

20:09.291 --> 20:10.751
Your mom is having the baby now.

20:10.793 --> 20:13.212
See? Was that so hard?

20:14.296 --> 20:16.256
Now, Hal, I don't want you

20:14.296 --> 20:16.256
to panic.

20:16.298 --> 20:17.508
You drive safely.

20:17.550 --> 20:19.552
There's no reason to rush.

20:19.593 --> 20:22.180
Rush? Come on.

20:19.593 --> 20:22.180
You know me

20:19.593 --> 20:22.180
better than that.

20:22.221 --> 20:23.472
Find your brother!

20:23.514 --> 20:26.559
So, I'm just going

20:23.514 --> 20:26.559
to make myself some tea

20:26.600 --> 20:27.977
and relax until you get here.

20:28.019 --> 20:29.269
Good idea.

20:29.311 --> 20:31.271
You know, chamomile

20:29.311 --> 20:31.271
always relaxes me.

20:31.313 --> 20:33.273
Reese! Damn it,

20:31.313 --> 20:33.273
Reese, where are you?!

20:33.315 --> 20:34.942
I'm thinking

20:33.315 --> 20:34.942
of taking Sixth Street home.

20:34.984 --> 20:36.694
You want me to stop

20:34.984 --> 20:36.694
and pick up some ice cream?

20:36.736 --> 20:38.278
Reese!

20:36.736 --> 20:38.278
Where are you?

20:38.320 --> 20:41.323
(muffled):

20:38.320 --> 20:41.323
Over here.

20:38.320 --> 20:41.323
Reese?!

20:41.365 --> 20:43.117
I'm inside

20:41.365 --> 20:43.117
the giant violin case.

20:43.159 --> 20:44.368
Damn it!

20:43.159 --> 20:44.368
Get him out of there.

20:45.703 --> 20:47.287
So, is that a yes

20:45.703 --> 20:47.287
on the ice cream?

20:47.329 --> 20:48.288
No, I'm fine.

20:48.330 --> 20:50.290
Just come on home... carefully.

20:50.332 --> 20:52.210
Oh.

20:50.332 --> 20:52.210
Sure thing.

20:52.251 --> 20:53.711
Honey, can you hold on a second?

20:53.753 --> 20:54.879
Ow!

20:54.921 --> 20:56.089
(grunts)

20:56.130 --> 20:58.007
Hey, what are you doing?

20:58.049 --> 21:00.259
Boys, run!

21:02.344 --> 21:03.596
The boys send their love, too.

21:03.637 --> 21:05.014
Hey! Hey, you

21:03.637 --> 21:05.014
come back here!

21:05.056 --> 21:07.391
Your kid ran off

21:05.056 --> 21:07.391
with my $600 tuxedo!

21:07.433 --> 21:09.685
So, we're just pulling out

21:07.433 --> 21:09.685
of the garage right now.

21:09.727 --> 21:10.978
Got it on the oldies station.

21:11.020 --> 21:12.312
They're doing

21:11.020 --> 21:12.312
a Beatles "A" to "Z."

21:12.354 --> 21:14.398
Can you think of a Beatles song

21:12.354 --> 21:14.398
that starts with "Z"?

21:14.440 --> 21:15.482
'Cause, frankly, I can't.

21:15.524 --> 21:16.734
Hal...

21:16.776 --> 21:18.819
You sound funny.

21:16.776 --> 21:18.819
Is everything okay?

21:18.861 --> 21:20.571
Yeah, just turning onto Maple.

21:20.613 --> 21:21.906
(whimpers)

21:21.948 --> 21:24.117
Hey, the gas station

21:21.948 --> 21:24.117
by the church

21:24.158 --> 21:26.160
stopped selling diesel.

21:29.163 --> 21:30.998
REESE:

21:29.163 --> 21:30.998
Ow!

21:31.040 --> 21:32.291
Shotgun!

21:33.251 --> 21:34.794
(grunts)

21:34.835 --> 21:36.378
Wow, honey, you wouldn't believe

21:34.835 --> 21:36.378
the huge pothole

21:36.420 --> 21:38.214
we just went over.

21:38.256 --> 21:40.216
Let's go, Dad!

21:40.258 --> 21:42.176
Oh! I can't find the keys!

21:42.218 --> 21:43.594
Keys?

21:43.636 --> 21:45.429
Where the hell

21:43.636 --> 21:45.429
are the keys?!

21:45.471 --> 21:46.513
REESE:

21:45.471 --> 21:46.513
I got 'em.

21:46.555 --> 21:47.723
Now let's go!

21:47.765 --> 21:49.558
(gasps)

21:49.600 --> 21:50.935
Hal?

21:50.977 --> 21:52.853
Honey, can I call you back?
